    "description": "<p>China Civil Engineering Construction Corporation Branch Office Singapore is a subsidiary of China Civil Engineering Construction Corporation , a state-owned enterprise whose business scope covers most of the civil engineering works such as railways, bridges, roads and buildings.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The corporation is consistently listed among the top 250 international contractors by Engineering News Record (ENR), and its latest ranking in 2012, is No. 71 with total revenue of 1.4 billion USD. Through the establishment of various subsidiaries in over 40 countries, the business activities of the corporation have expanded into over 60 regions and countries in Asia Pacific, Africa, Europe and America.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Being a new subsidiary of the corporation,&nbsp; China Civil Engineering Construction Corporation Branch Office Singapore was established in December of 2013 to further strengthen its presence in Southeast Asia region.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In collaboration with the parent company, we will provide construction services in terms of general building works as well as specialist building services such as piling work and structural steel work.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our future plans will include all types of construction services.</p>",
